Okay, I'll explain. I came into Scorponok's lab, and my scanners 
showed that the box on the table was the device. So I grabbed it. 
Just then my signal masker ran out of energy and the security guns 
came on and I hid up in the rafters. Than Battera came along to 
investigate but I got her to join me and betray Hell Beast by 
offering her a ticket hom. THAN Hell Beast, Mosquitor and the others 
came in.
